# Study Feature Tab (shared)

Study tabs (explanation, blank-study, quiz P1, etc.) share this shell inside the study workspace.

## Layout

- Split-pane: PDF left, feature panel right — [`StudySplitLayout`](src/features/study/components/StudySplitLayout.tsx)
- Shell: `StudyShell`, tabs via `StudyFeatureTabs`, header via `StudyWorkspaceHeader`
- Page/highlight sync: `StudyWorkspaceContext` (`setPage`, `setHighlightPage`)

## Generate panel empty state

When no result exists yet:

- Centered column with `max-w-generate-panel`
- Feature icon (`size-icon-xl`), title, short description
- Segmented option groups (`SegmentedOptionGroup`) for generate settings
- Primary generate CTA at bottom; show loading via `Loader2` on button

Mirror this pattern across explanation and blank-study tabs.

## Generate error (inline retry)

On AI generate failure, use `GenerateErrorAlert` — fixed message "분석에 실패했습니다" + 재시도 button. Do NOT expose raw `err.message` in UI.

## On-demand AI

- Upload extracts PDF text only — no explanation, blanks, or quiz on upload
- User clicks generate to create explanation / blanks / quiz content

## Feature-specific rules

- Explanation: `.cursor/rules/features/explanation.mdc` (add when working on explanation)
- Blank study: `.cursor/rules/features/blank-study.mdc`
